_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999998176463, \"rank\": 9.666672198626058e-11, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 756, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999344627234, \"rank\": 6.553521277776262e-08, \"text\": \"Moscow 1980\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1980_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Lincolnshire-born star\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympic Games\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 702}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"his best finish\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Capes travelled to Russia as a big medal hope so later admitted his performance in Moscow left him 'numbed with disappointment'.\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 925, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.718568811191872, \"rank\": 0.3484169711640319, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"score\": 0.9999824149865658, \"rank\": 1.7439925235481957e-05, \"text\": \"Moscow\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moscow\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Capes\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"a big medal hope\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 842}, {\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \